descriptionHtml:
Skimpy Glass Armor for CBBE V3 Slim.  This is a modification of the CBBE Daedric Female Armor created by Laxi2610 combined with some parts of the Skimpy Glass Armor created by Killer Keos. Enjoy!

This armor is a replacement for the existing Glass Armor.
